Notes
-----
This is still experimental. The helper path should reduce playback-time decode
work because every frame is already materialized before playback starts, but it
will increase initial load time and RAM usage. Large-file performance should be
tested with the user's real high-resolution GIF set before replacing the
installed GIF Viewer executable.
